Trade/Device Name(s): CareSens N Voice Multi Blood Glucose Monitoring System
CareSens N Multi Blood Glucose Test Strips
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): CareSens N Voice Multi Blood Glucose Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for CareSens N Voice Multi Blood Glucose Monitoring System for quantitative blood glucose measurement in multiple-patient professional healthcare settings
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from fingertips and alternative sites in professional healthcare settings for multiple-patient use as an aid to monitor diabetes control; not for diagnosis, screening, neonates, or use by visually impaired persons.
